description: Bonava AB engages in the development and sale of sustainable housing units. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 2,070 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-06-09. The firm operates as a developer of housing units to consumers and investors in Sweden, Germany, Finland, Denmark, Norway, the Russian Federation, Estonia and Latvia. In Germany, the Company's offering is targeted at consumers and investors through both single-family houses and multi-family houses. The firm operates on the basis of an own-produced construction system in Germany, which is used in all new construction, thus enabling an efficient construction process. In Estonia and Latvia, the Company’s offering is primarily targeted at consumers, based on multi-family houses. In Russia, it operates solely in Saint Petersburg region with offering comprises of multi-family houses.
name: Bonava AB (publ)
